column5: Happy Thanksgiving to you and your family
Happy Thanksgiving to WC members and all the protectors of our country.
Since you're posting on the Canada thread, I assume you mean Happy Belated Thanksgiving. Ours was on October 9th........but have yourselves a good one south of the border!
Posting for the members South of the Border!
I enjoyed one of each. Nashville this month and 18 miles north of Red Lake last month. I've doubled up a bunch of times. Enjoyed every one of them.
